## Smart Contract Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[ArenaCore] -->|triggerPriceUpdate| B[PriceOracle]
    A -->|updatePositions| C[PortfolioManager]
    A -->|updateRankings| D[Leaderboard]
    C -->|react| E[MomentumStrategy]
    C -->|react| F[MeanReversionStrategy]
    C -->|react| G[ArbitrageStrategy]
    C -->|react| H[RiskParityStrategy]
    C -->|react| I[RLStrategy]
    B -->|PriceUpdated event| J[ReactiveStrategyHandler]
    J -->|auto-trigger| C
    J -->|auto-trigger| D
    D -->|reads stats| C
```

